name: Time as Universal Flow of Consciousness
description:
9 LORDS OF TIME & DESTINY series #1

What is Time? Where it is? How do we know we are alive and not dreaming from far apart?

Are you aware of being? Are you present?

We all are lost time travelers recovering memory.

The Bolontikus according the Maya culture are the 9 LORDS OF TIME & DESTINY, guardians of the underworld, wisdom keepers of the inner realm of Time.

To know them is to die to who we think we are, are yo ready?
